General Galvez: "Domdra, you're there, aren't you! Proceed as
planned!"

Strategist Domdra: "As a parting gift to a fool like you, let me
enlighten you."
Strategist Domdra: "It's quite simple. I wanted to get rid of you."

Strategist Domdra: "For me to become the king of darkness, you were in

General Galvez: "What are you saying! You plan to betray Zai-Dag, to
betray Lord Da-Gnoa!?"

Strategist Domdra: "Betray? Foh foh foh. I am merely acting for my own
sake."

Strategist Domdra: "Once you are gone, Da-Gnoa will be alone. Then I
will visit with my excellent Zai-Borgs."

Strategist Domdra: "If I report that Pony-Ceres has been eliminated,
even he will have a moment of vulnerability."

Strategist Domdra: "After all, the greatest threat will have been
removed."

Strategist Domdra: "The Zai-Borgs that I have modified will not miss
that opportunity. They will surely finish off Da-Gnoa."

General Galvez: "So reviving the Zai-Borg and approaching me was all
part of your plan!"

Strategist Domdra: "Soon, this place will be blown away by the bombs

Strategist Domdra: "Pony-Ceres, please disappear along with this

Strategist Domdra: "It's futile. There is no escape from this curse."

parameters: Ginga: "Sorry to keep you waiting, Yui!"

Pony-Celeste: "What do you mean 'sorry to keep you waiting'?! I was
worried! You dummy, Ginga, dummy!!"
Pony-Celeste: "Ah, sorry... I didn't mean to!"

Ginga: "But thank you! You really waited for me because you believed
in me, didn't you?"
Pony-Celeste: "Ginga, it's okay to rely on you, right...?"

Pony-Celeste: "No, that's not it! I want to rely on Ginga. Just having

Ginga: "I've also gained courage from Yui to get this far."
Ginga: "Look, this is the crucial moment. Lift your head up!"

Ginga: "Everyone will worry if the invincible Pony-Celeste makes such
a face."
Ginga: "Besides, a sad face doesn't suit you, Yui."
Ginga: "Stay as my beloved Yui, the one I always know."
